    <h2 id="key-ingredients">Key Ingredients in Stress Relief Gummies</h2>

    <p>Not all stress gummies are formulated equally. The difference between a product that measurably reduces cortisol and one that delivers a placebo effect comes down to specific ingredients at clinically validated doses. These are the five compounds with the strongest evidence base for stress management in supplement form.</p>

    <div class="info-cards">
