        <strong>Ashwagandha KSM-66</strong>
        <p>The most clinically studied adaptogen for stress. A full-spectrum root extract standardized to 5% withanolides. Multiple RCTs show 23-30% cortisol reduction at 300-600mg daily. Takes 2-4 weeks for cumulative benefits. The gold standard for long-term stress management.</p>
      </div>
